== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== Bibliography and further reading on pre-Columbian Bogot\u00e1 ==\n\n=== Pre-Muisca ===\n* {{cite LSA |last=[[Gonzalo Correal Urrego|Correal Urrego]] |first=Gonzalo | year=1990 |title=Evidencias culturales durante el Pleistocene y Holoceno de Colombia \u2013 Cultural evidences during the Pleistocene and Holocene of Colombia |journal=Revista de Arqueolog\u00eda Americana |volume=1 |pages=69\u201389 |url=http://peru.inka.free.fr/Runapacha/pleiscol.pdf |language=es |accessdate=2016-07-08}}\n\n=== Economy ===\n* {{cite LSA |last=[[List of Muisca research institutes|Arg\u00fcello Garc\u00eda]] |first=Pedro Mar\u00eda |year=2015 |type=PhD |title=Subsistence economy and chiefdom emergence in the Muisca area. A study of the Valle de Tena (PhD) |url=http://d-scholarship.pitt.edu/24491/1/Arguello_P._Subsistence_economy.pdf |publisher=[[University of Pittsburgh]] |pages=1\u2013193 |accessdate=2016-07-08}}\n* {{cite LSA |last=[[List of Muisca research institutes|Francis]] |first=John Michael |year=1993 |title=\"Muchas hipas, no minas\" The Muiscas, a merchant society: Spanish misconceptions and demographic change (M.A.) |type=M.A. |publisher=[[University of Alberta]] |pages=1\u2013118 |accessdate=2016-07-08}}\n\n=== Society & ''[[tunjo]]s'' ===\n* {{cite LSA |last=[[Jago Cooper|Cooper]] |first=Jago |last2=[[Carl Henrik Langebaek|Langebaek]] |first2=Carl Henrik |year=2013 |title=The Lost Kingdoms of South America \u2013 Episode 3 \u2013 Lands of Gold |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_sovvzUAVoA |accessdate=2016-07-14}}\n* {{cite LSA |last=[[Jorge Gamboa Mendoza|Gamboa Mendoza]] |first=Jorge |year=2016 |title=Los muiscas, grupos ind\u00edgenas del Nuevo Reino de Granada. Una nueva propuesta sobre su organizac\u00edon socio-pol\u00edtica y su evoluc\u00edon en el siglo XVI \u2013 The Muisca, indigenous groups of the New Kingdom of Granada. A new proposal on their social-political organization and their evolution in the 16th century |url=https